" COMMANDS
" =====================================================================
command! ZVnor call s:CallZealNormally("<cword>")
command! ZVkey call s:CallZealWithKeyword()
command! ZVkeyDoc call s:CallZealWithKeywordAndDocset()
command! -range ZVvis call s:CallZealWithSelection()


